Package: indi-atik
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libindi1, libatik
Description: INDI Driver for Atik cameras and filter wheels.
 Driver for Atik cameras and filter wheels.
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.

Package: indi-atik-dbg
Priority: extra
Section: debug
Architecture: any
Depends: indi-atik (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: INDI Driver for Atik cameras and filter wheels.
 Driver for Atik cameras and filter wheels.
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.
 This package contains the debug symbols for the this driver, useful to investigate problems in INDI.
